## Frequently Asked Questions (FAQs)

<b> 1. What services does Your Dream Technologies offer?</b>
We provide complete digital solutions including website design & development, WordPress development, eCommerce development, mobile app development, SEO, digital marketing, UI/UX design, and more.

<b> 2. How much does a website cost in Varanasi?</b>
The cost depends on your requirements such as design complexity, features, and functionality. We offer affordable and customized pricing based on your business needs.

<b> 3. How long does it take to develop a website?</b>
A basic website can take 5–10 days, while advanced or eCommerce websites may take 2–4 weeks depending on project scope.

<b> 4. Do you provide SEO services along with website development?</b>
Yes, we offer complete SEO services including on-page, off-page, and technical SEO to help your website rank higher on search engines.

<b> 5. Will my website be mobile-friendly?</b>
Absolutely. All our websites are fully responsive and optimized for mobile, tablet, and desktop devices.

<b> 6. Can you redesign my existing website?</b>
Yes, we can redesign your current website to improve its design, performance, user experience, and SEO.

<b> 7. Do you offer eCommerce website development?</b>
Yes, we specialize in creating secure and scalable eCommerce websites with payment gateway integration and user-friendly interfaces.

<b> 8. What technologies do you use for development?</b>
We use modern technologies such as WordPress, Laravel, HTML5, CSS3, JavaScript, and various frameworks to build high-quality solutions.

<b> 9. Do you provide support and maintenance after project completion?
Yes, we offer ongoing support and maintenance services to ensure your website runs smoothly and stays updated.

